-width: 1240px) 700px, (min-width: 675px) 620px, calc(100vw - 40px)\" data-srcset=\"https://fashionista.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cfl_progressive%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_380/MjEyOTk2NzA5OTAxNDExODQ5/sonage-brand-bio.jpg 380w, https://fashionista.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cfl_progressive%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_620/MjEyOTk2NzA5OTAxNDExODQ5/sonage-brand-bio.jpg 620w, https://fashionista.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cfl_progressive%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_700/MjEyOTk2NzA5OTAxNDExODQ5/sonage-brand-bio.jpg 700w\"/\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"sonage-brand-bio\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://fashionista.com/.image/t_share/MjEyOTk2NzA5OTAxNDExODQ5/sonage-brand-bio.jpg\" data-src=\"https://fashionista.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cfl_progressive%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_700/MjEyOTk2NzA5OTAxNDExODQ5/sonage-brand-bio.jpg\" height=\"1311\" width=\"1311\" srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7\" itemprop=\"contentUrl url\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/phoenix-picture\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003e\u003cp itemprop=\"author\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003ePhoto: Courtesy of Sonäge\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://fashionista.com/tag/brand-bio\"\u003e\u003cem\u003eBrand Bio\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cem\u003e is Fashionista\u0026#39;s guide to the best independent fashion and \u003ca href=\"https://fashionista.com/beauty\"\u003ebeauty\u003c/a\u003e brands — a resource for retailers, job seekers, B2B companies and consumers alike. If you\u0026#39;d like your brand to be featured, \u003ca href=\"https://fashionista.com/page/brand-form\"\u003efill out this form\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eSonäge\u003c/strong\u003e\u003cbr/\u003eHeadquarters: Santa Monica, CA\u003cbr/\u003eE-commerce: \u003ca href=\"https://fave.co/4hPMEC4\" rel=\"noopener\" onclick=\"return phoenixTrackClickEvent(this, event);\" target=\"_blank\"\u003esonage.com\u003c/a\u003e\u003cbr/\u003eSocial Media: \u003ca href=\"https://www.instagram.com/sonageskincare/?hl=en\" rel=\"noopener\" onclick=\"return phoenixTrackClickEvent(this, event);\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eInstagram\u003c/a\u003e / \u003ca href=\"https://www.tiktok.com/@sonageskincare?lang=en\" rel=\"noopener\" onclick=\"return phoenixTrackClickEvent(this, event);\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eTikTok\u003c/a\u003e / \u003ca href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sonageskincare/\" rel=\"noopener\" onclick=\"return phoenixTrackClickEvent(this, event);\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eFacebook\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eWhat: \u003c/strong\u003eA California-based \u003ca href=\"https://fashionista.com/tag/skin-care\"\u003eskin-care\u003c/a\u003e brand that focuses on effective products made with natural alternatives that aim to deliver a soothing, spa-like experience.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003ePrice Range: \u003c/strong\u003e$20-$70\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eFounder:\u003c/strong\u003e Anisha Khanna\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eOrigin Story:\u003c/strong\u003e Inspired by her upbringing in India and Ayurvedic traditions, Anisha Khanna founded her skin-care brand Sonäge in 1994. Sonäge gets its name from the French expression \u0026#34;Bien porter son âge,\u0026#34; which translates to, \u0026#34;To look good for one\u0026#39;s age.\u0026#34; \u003c/p\u003e\u003csection id=\"phx-3\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eScroll to Continue\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv id=\"phx-5\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ch2 role=\"heading\" aria-level=\"2\"\u003eRecommended Articles\u003c/h2\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/section\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe \u0026#34;spa-grade\u0026#34; brand balances skin-care science with curated botanical ingredients. The formulas draw on Ayurvedic ingredients and modern science to create products using natural options such as burdock root, honeysuckle and tea